"┌ pgtop · test — Top Queries ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐"
"│ Activity │ Locks │ Top Queries │ Replication │ Databases │ Tables │ Waits                                            │"
"│ TPS: — ─────────────────────────────── Active: — ───────────────────────────── Cache hit: — ─────────────────────────│"
"│                                                                                                                      │"
"│                                                                                                                      │"
"│                                                                                                                      │"
"│  pg_stat_statements extension is not installed.                                                                      │"
"│                                                                                                                      │"
"│  This tab tracks normalized query statistics — calls, total                                                          │"
"│  time, mean time. To enable:                                                                                         │"
"│                                                                                                                      │"
"│    1. Add to postgresql.conf:                                                                                        │"
"│       shared_preload_libraries = 'pg_stat_statements'                                                                │"
"│                                                                                                                      │"
"│    2. Restart Postgres.                                                                                              │"
"│                                                                                                                      │"
"│    3. In your database:                                                                                              │"
"│       CREATE EXTENSION pg_stat_statements;                                                                           │"
"│                                                                                                                      │"
"│  For docker-compose: set `command:` with `-c shared_preload_libraries=...`                                           │"
"│  and use /docker-entrypoint-initdb.d for CREATE EXTENSION on init.                                                   │"
"│                                                                                                                      │"
"│ q quit  ·  1234567 tabs  ·  ↑↓ move  ·  x/X export                                                                   │"
"└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘"
